{"tid":769501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整容後變男神 泰國男成熱爆網紅","createTime":"2018-08-06T08:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T18:12:45.000Z","uid":3189,"like":58,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"d82f89ee5a480aba98b3422325b39227dd8ffd22","tid":769501,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/16443302775abc74136dbf0_7602193145ac21973bb405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F16443302775abc74136dbf0_7602193145ac21973bb405.jpg&h=5a03a1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整容後變男神 泰國男成熱爆網紅<br />\n<br />\n成日有人話「Your face, your fate」其實一個人的外貌真係好鬼重要，泰國有一位30歲男子金民豪，因為其貌不揚到直頭係有啲樣衰，所以多年來慘遭白眼及種種不公平的對待，而且之前有27年都識唔到女朋友，所以決定放心一搏去整容，依家搖身一變成為網紅&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n呢位叫金民豪的泰國哥哥仔，天生鼻翼大、鼻孔仲大，再加上唇厚、外凸等，除咗經常被人嫌醜，佢本身打算報讀泰國當地藝術學校，都因為個樣就喺第一關面試被淘汰。講到愛情方面，大家都應該想像到，話說佢直到27歲，都識唔到女朋友，就算主動告白都多次被拒絕&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050113_18808334265abc72591fbd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050113_18808334265abc72591fbd6.jpg&h=cad9e087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050112_13041600715abc7268b2e0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050112_13041600715abc7268b2e0a.jpg&h=7ae3cb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊儲錢邊整容 三年做30次手術<br />\n<br />\n成日話「你的樣子如何，你的日子也必如何」金民豪多年來受咗唔少白眼，仲有種種不公平的對待，所以佢下定決心要整容！但係佢家境唔係咁好，金民豪只能邊儲錢邊整容，三年間做咗30次女手術，用咗逾30萬泰銖。依家佢已經變成一位型男！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050111_15283610355abc726e18b27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050111_15283610355abc726e18b27.jpg&h=e08da382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整容男神熱爆網絡<br />\n經過大刀闊斧的改造，金民豪幾乎完全變咗另一個人，帥氣十足，行出街真係會以為係邊個韓國明星！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050105_8133413015abc7274cb555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050105_8133413015abc7274cb555.jpg&h=2d7d4a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050106_2099389705abc727aa53cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050106_2099389705abc727aa53cf.jpg&h=fc7a992e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金民豪依家除咗變成當地網紅，仲吸納唔少女粉絲，佢透露連以前自己暗戀過的女仔都主動約佢去街！果然「 Your face, your fate」係無錯的&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichub.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3050107_6271851355abc7282e9d09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichub.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F3050107_6271851355abc7282e9d09.jpg&h=0840bddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/%E6%BD%AE%E8%81%9E/%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9-%E7%94%B7%E7%A5%9E-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85/6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25A5%259E-%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585%2F6%2F&d=1rt2mGOf%2BUhkdsep%2Bp%2FSyQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=20d622fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/%E6%BD%AE%E8%81%9E/%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9-%E7%94%B7%E7%A5%9E-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85/6/</a>"},{"pid":"222dd2f4afd157b427cf8b467c6b2aebbe31f3ea","tid":769501,"uid":7043,"like":216,"dislike":2,"score":214,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"整容真係改變命運<br />\n將hard mode 換番去做easy mode 玩"},{"pid":"3be305baf4965c86fead